SIMPLIFY TOOL
================

INTRODUCTION
************
Simplify is the tool that can simplify the Administrative Role Based Access Control model (ARBAC).

INSTALLATION
************
Please refer to the INSTALL file (in the same directory)

USAGE
*****
You can invoke the tool by using
	simplify FILE

Detail can be found by invoking --help option

WEB
***
The tool can be found on VAC main website: http://users.ecs.soton.ac.uk/gp4/VAC.html

